Author: BadaBeast
Text: I don’t think I’ve experienced any consequences YET but I’m terrified of what’ll happen when they do come :(

Author: bigLlittleL
Text: I feel you- I don’t even think that I could seek more intense help (treatment center level) unless a. My body was truly failing (major organs) or I was less than 100 lbs. why that number? Who knows? I’m so sorry that you feel similarly- it sucks to feel like a fake when even that feeling is disordered.
